"> </span><span class=\"n\">HasDistribNeg</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">D</span><span class=\"bp\">ˣ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Units</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">instHasDistribNeg</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- Where any nonzero element is a unit</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">check</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ne</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">isUnit</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
